stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Created
  Created --> Pulling: image / artifact scheduled
  Pulling --> Loading: container starts
  Loading --> Warming: weights loaded, warmup running
  Warming --> Ready: readiness probe passes
  Ready --> Canary: receive canary traffic
  Canary --> Stable: rollout gate passed
  Canary --> RollingBack: gate failed
  Stable --> Draining: rollout / scale down / maintenance
  Draining --> Stopped: no active streams
  RollingBack --> Draining
  Stopped --> [*]
